 public FFI\CDatanullFFI::new
 FFI\CTypestringtype
 boolowned&true;
 boolpersistent&false;



 Creates a native data structure of the given C type.
 Any type declared for the instance is allowed.

&reftitle.returnvalues;


 Returns the freshly created FFI\CData object,
 or &null; on failure.

